      <img src="spotlight-biblia2.jpg" alt="Cover of the Spotlight: The Bible series" class="series-cover">
      <p>"Spotlight: The Bible" is an extraordinary literary trilogy that dives deep into the heart of the Judeo-Christian religious narrative, revealing a unique and daring journey. Across three thrilling volumes (two already available), this series challenges conventional beliefs and uncovers the deepest secrets of the Holy Scriptures.</p>
      <p>From the beginning of Creation to the agony of Babylonian captivity, "Spotlight: The Bible" takes us on a fascinating journey through the events and characters that shaped our spiritual understanding. What makes this series remarkable is its boldness in questioning dogmas and exposing truths buried under layers of myth and interpretation.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="book">
      <img src="adao-eva.jpg" alt="Book cover of Adam and Eve">
      <h3>Adam & Eve: Secrets Unveiled</h3>
      <p>An irreverent journey to the origins of Evil. In this book, Raphael Sousa weaves together biblical myths and ancient cosmogonies to reveal what was never told about Eden â€“ the serpent, Lilith, Satan, fallen angels, and giants. Nothing here is simplistic: the fall wasn't just disobedience, it was the birth of human pain.</p>
