    <section class="book">
      <img src="historia-biblia.jpg" alt="Book cover of The True History of the Bible">
      <h3>The True History of the Bible</h3>
      <p>Reveals what tradition tried to erase: the Bible was not born complete or pure. Raphael Sousa unveils the forgotten past of a nomadic, illiterate people who, centuries after exile, rewrote their history from ruins and shame. Who really wrote the sacred texts? Which voices were silenced? Amid betrayals, censorship, and the invention of a tribal God, this book dismantles myths and invites readers into raw truth.</p>
      <a href="https://www.amazon.com.br/Verdadeira-Hist%C3%B3ria-B%C3%ADblia-Spotlight-Livro-ebook/dp/B0CLL64K7P" class="cta" target="_blank">Buy on Amazon</a>
